# 大 ONNX 模型 (超 GitHub 100 MB 单文件上限，避开 LFS 开销)：
# DINOv3 backbone (1.2 GB) — scripts/export_dinov3_backbone.py
# CLIPIQA+ (293 MB) / HyperIQA (104 MB) — scripts/export_iqa_onnx.py
# 分发时由 electron-builder extraResources 打包进安装包
engine/models/dinov3_backbone.onnx
engine/models/clipiqa_plus.onnx
engine/models/hyperiqa.onnx
